{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957350/extras/banner-1.png?t=1714515575\" /><br><br>Dive into this neon-lit, dystopian world as an Inquisitor detective unravelling the mystery behind a series of murders. This game is the first of its kind: a thrilling fusion of rogue-lite randomization and a traditional point-and-click adventure!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957350/extras/ss-box-01.png?t=1714515575\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957350/extras/banner-2.png?t=1714515575\" /><br><br>Every case is set in a sprawling high-density Megabuilding, where you will meet and question various Citizens in order to uncover the truth. Explore each floor of the Megabuilding, from grimy bars to lavish penthouses, in search of clues and suspects. With each playthrough, face new challenges and unpredictable twists, ensuring no two investigations are alike.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957350/extras/ss-box-02.png?t=1714515575\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957350/extras/banner-3.png?t=1714515575\" /><br><br>Utilize your wits and gather evidence to crack the case before time runs out and corruption consumes the city. Can you navigate this unpredictable, treacherous world and bring some justice to its oppressed Citizens?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957350/extras/ss-box-03.png?t=1714515575\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1714515575","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957350/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=17